msgstr "Kuidas filtreerida rämpsposti &imap; serveris?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:108
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<emphasis>Symptom:</emphasis> You intend moving on to reading your mail "
#| "from an &imap; server, and wonder how filtering and spam handling will "
#| "occur?"
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Problem:</emphasis> You intend to read your mail from an &IMAP; "
"server, and wonder how filtering and spam handling will occur."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Sümptomid</emphasis>: kavatsed hakata oma kirju lugema &imap; "
"serveris ning mõtled, kuidas käib seal filtreerimine ja rämpsposti "
