#: faq.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Why did &kmail; regenerate the index of a folder?"
msgstr "Miks &kmail; regenereerib kausta indeksi?"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:286
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kmail; regenerates the index of a folder whenever the index appears to "
#| "be out of date, &ie; whenever the contents of a folder are newer than the "
#| "index. &kmail; regenerates the index in this case in order to prevent the "
#| "loss or corruption of messages. Unfortunately, currently-deleted messages "
#| "might reappear and message flags (like important, etc.) might be lost "
#| "when the index is regenerated."
msgid ""
"&kmail; regenerates the index of a folder whenever the index appears to be "
"out of date, &ie; whenever the contents of a folder are newer than the "
"index. &kmail; regenerates the index in this case in order to prevent the "
"loss or corruption of messages."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; regenereerib kausta indeksi alati, kui see paistab olevat aegunud, "
"&ie; kui kausta sisu on uuem kui indeks. &kmail; regenereerib sellisel juhul "
"indeksi, et vältida kirjade kadu või riknemist. Paraku võivad seetõttu "
"taasilmuda äsjakustutatud kirjad ning lipukesed (nt. 'tähtis' jne.) kaduma "
"minna, kui indeks regenereeritakse."

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:290
