"guilabel>ning lülita sisse <xref linkend=\"configure-composer-general-append-"
"signature\"/>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"How do I set up &Sendmail; to work with &kmail; if I have a dial-up "
